I decided to delete the other cards out of fear.
This is a record of the events of 11/55/21. The following is all I have left after the attack.
After Tinkering with what I thought would be mundane front end coding at the end of the night, I saw a faint glowing dot on the screen.
At first it was a soft glow, But after a minute it started to pulsate with a regular vibrancy equated to pulsars in distant galaxies.
As I moused over the dot it would make another dot appear.
Soon there were dots all over my screen. The pulsing for each dot was in unison.
I felt a strange feeling come over me as I started to hear voices chanting in strange tongues.
